query:
SELECT se.*, f.nome as formandoNome, t.codigo as turmaCodigo, e.dataEvento
FROM servicos_execucao se
JOIN formandos f ON se.formandoId = f.id
JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id
LEFT JOIN eventos e ON se.eventoId = e.id
ORDER BY se.id DESC LIMIT 20
